newsitem.title: SINGAPORE: Singapore bunker final report and prices- Sept 19.
newsitem.headline: Singapore bunker final report and prices- Sept 19.

text.p: DELIVERED U.S.$/TONNE) 380 CST 180 CST MDO GAS OIL

COMMENTS - Singapore bunker indications on Thursday were wide-ranged, although within Wednesday's levels, with some majors hiking offers, citing scarce supplies. Bunker 380-cst was quoted at $119-$120 by majors with independents at a low of $115. Bunker 180-cst cargoes edged lower and was traded at $121. Some traders said the high offers were for prompt supplies. MDO and gas oil was lower at $202-$208 and $218-$220 respectively.
